ygData.messageBody:
Ok, I need some help here. I am a 12 monk on
Veeshan and there is NO WERE for me to hunt! I have tried
kerras island, but I die conesitently, and have actually
LOST XP. I have tried the E and W commons, but cant
solo there, there is nothing worth killing ANYWAYS,
besides dervs, and I have tried Black Burrow, but that
also sucks. What about the chessboard in Butcher
Block? What do you all think? I am open to ANY
suggestions...<br><br>Cerial<br>12TH Monk<br>Veeshan
